<translation id="7158975242722498086">Tizim administratori tomonidan Ecosia brauzeri <ph name="TARGET_URL_HOSTNAME"/> sahifasini <ph name="ALTERNATIVE_BROWSER_NAME"/> orqali ochiladigan qilib sozlangan.</translation>
